{"tid":2274462,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人幾首掛住佢個陣會聽嘅歌","createTime":"2020-11-06T12:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T12:34:55.000Z","uid":382861,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"ff76bf175b6be96c5d01f4e5261666e24fd7dbb7","tid":2274462,"uid":382861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"周杰倫&mdash;蒲公英的約定<br />\n而我已經分不清 你是友情還是錯過的愛情<br />\n<br />\n五月天&mdash;知足<br />\n如果我愛上 你的笑容 <br />\n要怎麼收藏 要怎麼擁有 <br />\n如果你快樂 不是為我 <br />\n會不會放手 其實才是擁有<br />\n<br />\n林一峰 &mdash; 一支煙的時間<br />\n讓那火機噠的一聲把快樂燃點 <br />\n隨著空中翻飛煙圈消散 <br />\n我亦明白 應怎打算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6e843a51a52edfb37849066d9ca03153388b20","tid":2274462,"uid":130591,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"誰活著未靠感覺做人才可悲<br />\n陪你到處吃街燈晚餐極歡喜<br />\n挽你手 也只因想挽手<br />\n決不因世俗看得起你<br />\n若笑著吃苦也餓不死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43887c55c1538a7c8ab760be8551d55520d9f976","tid":2274462,"uid":20914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"償還<br />\n約定"},{"pid":"71f3cd43bb230644f11036bfe4c15d69f890422c","tid":2274462,"uid":319704,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39c2ea43ba6b8cf2776a309b258323daf45371cd","tid":2274462,"uid":382861,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"71f3cd43bb230644f11036bfe4c15d69f890422c","tid":2274462,"uid":319704,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"我好想你 好想你 就深藏在心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a526ccfa3ea157f2999b49209af256bd5e56d8a2","tid":2274462,"uid":243351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"我們一起離開吧<br />\n<br />\nwake me up when september end"},{"pid":"da51a71b20531ba647a7909ad76370e74eb53ffa","tid":2274462,"uid":370263,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"原來這裡沒有你 原來世界沒有那麼美"},{"pid":"874f7ccf057294a27f5ac536a7809bf409344016","tid":2274462,"uid":350206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"第一個早晨<br />\n白日初昇 你在我面前 雖然你而家已經唔喺度<br />\n認真如初<br />\n留一輩子給你 承諾認真與你活一世 就算你唔喺度我仍然會留一輩子給你"},{"pid":"4cabb2de7ec52dcb4ff27f6e19dffd3cf5ca1778","tid":2274462,"uid":21139,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"茶沒有喝光早變酸 從來未熱戀已失戀<br />\n陪著你輕呼著煙圈 那纏繞怎麼可算短<br />\n你的衣裳今天的在穿 未留住你卻仍然溫暖"},{"pid":"6c9832471dbb0b73949fca5784c514bab5a6d06c","tid":2274462,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶沒有喝光早變酸 從來未熱戀已失戀<br />\n陪著你輕呼著煙圈 那纏繞怎麼可算短<br />\n你的衣裳今天我在穿 未留住你卻仍然溫暖</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7a0355abd392cfd6dc386ab820c208c3973fd703","tid":2274462,"uid":21963,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"心燒<br />\n黑洞<br />\n陰天快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2c374a42bc3b6b553fc74dc69b9d14516ccc79","tid":2274462,"uid":238504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"負親"},{"pid":"cbc5bc6e96d5f0b83db8dcfd50e151dc54adb275","tid":2274462,"uid":370479,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"幾分之幾 盧廣仲<br />\n那一天你走進了我的生命<br />\n謝謝你成為了我的幾分之幾"},{"pid":"ba832e2b521615c5d68b4074e0d4ba00f7ee9755","tid":2274462,"uid":189885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc5bc6e96d5f0b83db8dcfd50e151dc54adb275","tid":2274462,"uid":370479,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"幾分之幾 盧廣仲<br />\n那一天你走進了我的生命