18:11:03.000Z","msg":"天早灰藍 想告別 偏未晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一告別就好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4ce7440c0f6121e062481ed71a827efdecd505","tid":2274462,"uid":366810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T18:23:47.000Z","msg":"那些追憶本可一躍就過 <br />\n我偏喜歡給它一再折磨<br />\n其實滿懷執著 不甘心的一個是我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d96f38fba69208b48e0dedff855df0117f3a8a","tid":2274462,"uid":374818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>鄭中基-one more time </strong><br />\nOne More Time<br />\n其實想起了你我的心會暖<br />\nOne More Time<br />\n還是想起了你統統都已變<br />\n<br />\n<strong>AGA-Everyday</strong><br />\n何時能再一起怎樣說起<br />\n何時能記不起尤其是你<br />\n沒有給思念限期<br />\n明知再見 還是要空歡喜<br />\nEveryday just Everyday<br />\n站在原地 無奈激情已經死<br />\n不應提起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Zpecial- 深夜告別練習</strong><br />\n滑道上傾側倒退又轉身<br />\n我與妳一刻似是無限近<br />\n錯過若於此刻<br />\n終於都這樣陌生<br />\n月夜下彎身加快又企穩<br />\n每晚也不歸家找一個人<br />\n徐徐遺忘分針 於抱憾中覓尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cc7de2f55f105d690f0b5fb54e6ee2184f7d4d","tid":2274462,"uid":172321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"衛蘭 《驗傷》<br />\n是 是早知有今天<br />\n<br />\n《逃生門》<br />\n大門被你緊緊鎖上那一下..."},{"pid":"25459bca86418cb8c8721791e30b43012ef24fce","tid":2274462,"uid":357740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f22e3ef0523dbe48c8e02029da957b32c501115b","tid":2274462,"uid":193275,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:43:31.000Z","msg":"借火<br />\n金剛圈<br />\n尼古丁<br />\n一支煙的時間<br />\n愛我別走<br />\nrich brian - history"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T19:20:05.000Z","msg":"但我一口 又再接一口<br />\n輸給愛情 絕症"},{"pid":"be41c3dcd22bb189fd3ca5739960d7cf1e60d58e","tid":2274462,"uid":186051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T20:23:49.000Z","msg":"I hate you, I love you."},{"pid":"a66e9b9a62d91c18bbf19a2d2b667b30527c95f8","tid":2274462,"uid":150675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc5bc6e96d5f0b83db8dcfd50e151dc54adb275","tid":2274462,"uid":370479,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"幾分之幾 盧廣仲<br />\n那一天你走進了我的生命<br />\n謝謝你成為了我的幾分之幾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:02:02.000Z","msg":"呢排我都成日聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a9d538fc6458ff8237f039b638b173d87bf1f8","tid":2274462,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:13:39.000Z","msg":"Beauty and the beast<br />\n這是愛<br />\n一生所愛"},{"pid":"06a0f7721b2197763f30f5360ed53a0df591345f","tid":2274462,"uid":193044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1539e37e30ca417f48384eca716dacf08aeb433","tid":2274462,"uid":146482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"多一秒留戀　差一秒歷史改寫意義 <br />\n回憶的刺　想念痛多一次　只求不相見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:14:58.000Z","msg":"風箏 unreleased live version d 詞仲痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64e0e2d81921854d49f6433becf338ed6144313","tid":2274462,"uid":326848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:43:57.000Z","msg":"當世事再沒完美　可遠在歲月如歌中找你"},{"pid":"fadf35476e8d3fa22f0a5797b4fdbaed69cd578e","tid":2274462,"uid":29645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:56:01.000Z","msg":"就在八月知你住我家附近之後 <br />\n那夜經過大角咀你細訴小時候 <br />\n然後我們隔一兩週 便結伴公園夜遊 <br />\n潛入「嶺南之風」看不見四周  <br />\n但是我亦走不進你心裡頭 <br />\n某夜親吻到似變了男女朋友 <br />\n但是你從不愛拖手 只是放手進我衣袖 <br />\n代表只想取暖 是否？"},{"pid":"dbb4ba00622ba7d7542f7e556a31b89d8b06bb09","tid":2274462,"uid":217066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score